## Migration Checklist for New Components

When adding a new card/panel/section to the UI:

1. Use `className="card"` (or `className="card card--interactive"`) as the base
2. Add a domain-specific modifier class for any unique layout (e.g. `.card .my-widget`)
3. In the component CSS, define ONLY layout and animation rules under `.my-widget`
4. For sections/panels, use `.section` as the base class
5. Never import or duplicate token definitions — they are global

